3f-fb9d0de5d487--2021_0211_palais-des-thes_matcha-tea-set_gif-still_1x1_ty-mecham_09.jpg, https://images.food52.com/ak7VKalcfczoi9OTzP3ps9o2vIs=/750x750/filters:format(webp)/a09df19a-328f-4f6f-a93f-fb9d0de5d487--2021_0211_palais-des-thes_matcha-tea-set_gif-still_1x1_ty-mecham_09.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/g4PJHoM_siDqq98VMJhJKm2nyeA=/375x375/a09df19a-328f-4f6f-a93f-fb9d0de5d487--2021_0211_palais-des-thes_matcha-tea-set_gif-still_1x1_ty-mecham_09.jpg, https://images.food52.com/p2o6xD6EhynLusV1FI2tGuexqjA=/750x750/a09df19a-328f-4f6f-a93f-fb9d0de5d487--2021_0211_palais-des-thes_matcha-tea-set_gif-still_1x1_ty-mecham_09.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"964\" height=\"964\" data-expand=\"750\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/g4PJHoM_siDqq98VMJhJKm2nyeA=/375x375/a09df19a-328f-4f6f-a93f-fb9d0de5d487--2021_0211_palais-des-thes_matcha-tea-set_gif-still_1x1_ty-mecham_09.jpg, https://images.food52.com/p2o6xD6EhynLusV1FI2tGuexqjA=/750x750/a09df19a-328f-4f6f-a93f-fb9d0de5d487--2021_0211_palais-des-thes_matcha-tea-set_gif-still_1x1_ty-mecham_09.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n          \u003cspan\u003ePhoto by Ty Mecham\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n              \u003ch2\u003eHow to Store Matcha\u003c/h2\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eMatcha is sensitive to light, air, and heat and if you store it incorrectly, it can go bad quickly. In general, it doesn’t have the same shelf-life as other tea. You want to store it in an airtight container in the fridge to keep it fresh. It should be vibrant green; if it turns dull or brownish, it’s probably past its prime.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003ch2\u003eOur Favorite Matcha Powders\u003c/h2\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eWe’ve tested, read the reviews, and scrolled Reddit so you don’t have to. These are the top-rated matcha powders worth trying:\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003e• \u003ca href=\"https://ippodotea.com/collections/matcha?srsltid=AfmBOoqncsPuhyDgh33VeTGa0YNhOfRE4deaaIQXA-iYVwjcrwhY6haH\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIppodo Tea\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, from $19 – The gold standard for ceremonial matcha. It’s so good that the original ones are currently sold out due to demand.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003e• \u003ca href=\"https://www.jadeleafmatcha.com/collections/pure-matcha\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eJade Leaf\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, from $16 – A solid pick with affordable ceremonial options and a great starter kit. I also love their sweetened latte mixes, which I think is a great starting point for non-matcha drinkers.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003e• \u003ca href=\"https://rishi-tea.com/products/organic-barista-matcha?variant=44376696750330\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRishi Organic Everyday\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, $48 – Recommended by avid matcha drinkers for its balance and reliability. Plus, it’s available at a lot of different stores and a bunch of places online.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003e• \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Chamberlain-Coffee-Organic-Japanese-Gluten-Free/dp/B09H9V9881/ref=asc_df_B09H9V9881?mcid=121708035e373b73bc0c5346ca4463ad\u0026amp;hvocijid=11236506184613097585-B09H9V9881-\u0026amp;hvexpln=73\u0026amp;tag=hyprod-20\u0026amp;linkCode=df0\u0026amp;hvadid=721245378154\u0026amp;hvpos=\u0026amp;hvnetw=g\u0026amp;hvrand=11236506184613097585\u0026amp;hvpone=\u0026amp;hvptwo=\u0026amp;hvqmt=\u0026amp;hvdev=c\u0026amp;hvdvcmdl=\u0026amp;hvlocint=\u0026amp;hvlocphy=9021571\u0026amp;hvtargid=pla-2281435180258\u0026amp;th=1\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eChamberlain Coffee\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, $27 – Surprisingly great quality, even if you’re skeptical of influencer brands. You can also get a lot of the \u003ca href=\"https://chamberlaincoffee.com/collections/accessories\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eaccessories \u003c/a\u003e to go with.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003e• \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Naoki-Matcha-Superior-Ceremonial-Blend/dp/B01L2GW7SI/ref=sr_1_1_sspa?crid=1K1V6HAKCG5F1\u0026amp;dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.6kRtyvo2c7gk513P2dsP5-gtX6YzyQKKPzqEY-Za8SoQnXCb1EFe0Z8wn4EDug3stvvvgr_bEe-JeGI6pb1VYY32vH9Qo0f7Eto0qDSU-H6ru6s9o3IgpFWmQqKL2yaBJ6E9ZM9OgVNDDZ9XGrZaxjt4x1J9Xnst2Jd-DAhO2nfj4m0-r4UuAq1RsoiLir2bILiPQosbOvnity1qzB4fuUGc0sFs2_cKl98oIJG-hEgpOrAkvqCfy503ivWpzckQ-VNAZbxHi-hZtJqZM3PsTerP5mq3MUCgeMdt03SX9k8.Ky2DkLq3n7bZ_eIFlkUrJ7dTk3p9gizAlT5-zu8KIKs\u0026amp;dib_tag=se\u0026amp;keywords=naoki+matcha\u0026amp;qid=1746111070\u0026amp;s=grocery\u0026amp;sprefix=naoki+%2Cgrocery%2C173\u0026amp;sr=1-1-spons\u0026amp;sp_csd=d2lkZ2V0TmFtZT1zcF9hdGY\u0026amp;psc=1\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNaoki Matcha\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, $27 – Highly rated on Amazon, with over 5,000 glowing reviews and on pretty much every “best ever” list.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n\n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ca href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button\" data-pin-do=\"buttonPin\" data-pin-media=\"\" data-pin-custom=\"true\" data-ga-event=\"inPageInteraction\" data-ga-event-action=\"Pinterest Share\" data-ga-event-label=\"Article Body Image\" data-ga-destination-url=\"none\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16.9 20.8\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16.8 6.3C16.5 3.2 13.6.4 10.1.1 4.8-.5.1 2.7 0 7.9c0 2.4.8 4 2.9 4.8 1.5-1.5-.3-2.4-.5-4C2 4.3 7.1.1 11.7 2.9c3.2 1.9 2.6 9.9-1.2 10.7-.8.1-1.8-.1-2.1-.5-1.9-1.8 1.5-4.8.4-7.3-.9-2.1-3.6-.4-3.9 1.5-.2 1 .3 2 .3 2.9 0 2.1-1.3 5-1.7 7.1-.2.9-.3 2.6-.1 3.4h1.5c1-1.6 1.6-4.1 2.1-6.3.3-.2.5.4.7.6 1.8 1.4 5 .6 6.4-.7 2.1-1.7 3-5.2 2.7-8\" fill=\"currentColor\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n      \u003c/a\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0